{"tid":2495686,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"男生被指鐳射筆照警   陳慧敏: 手拎住擺明有意圖傷人　","createTime":"2021-04-19T10:27:23.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-19T13:50:11.000Z","uid":56115,"like":2,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"fd0eda84c87aa56bb09c0ba6454db29afe350207","tid":2495686,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T10:27:23.000Z","msg":"前年 9 月 24 日，大批示威者包圍旺角警署，14 歲女童等四人被控非法集結等罪，今（19 日）在西九龍裁判法院開審。首被告被指用鐳射筆照射警員，原本不認罪，裁判官陳慧敏看畢現場片段，認為片段清晰顯示其行為，反問辯方：「<span class=\"red\">揸枝咁強勁嘅筆，都搵唔到 intent（意圖）？射到警察眼睛，你覺得冇 intent？</span>」<span class=\"red\">首被告與律師商討後，下午最終承認三罪</span>。同案女童聽到他認罪一度哭泣，需離庭由家人安撫。其求情押至本周四（22 日）處理，期間以原有條件保釋。<br />\n<br />\n辯方不爭議各被告身份及當時在場。首被告蔡否認兩項非法集結及在公眾地方管有攻擊性武器罪，裁判官<span class=\"red\">陳慧敏認為，片段清楚顯示他用鐳射筆照射警員</span>；辯方同意首被告當時手持鐳射筆，但爭議傷人目的。裁判官聞言反問：「揸枝咁強勁嘅筆，都搵唔到 intent（意圖）？射到警察眼睛，你覺得冇 intent？」"},{"pid":"db64c5a0be8cdbf52bd5bf0fb13285d0ca7b3aa6","tid":2495686,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T10:27:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/court/9-24-%E5%A4%AA%E5%AD%90-19-%E6%AD%B2%E7%94%B7%E7%94%9F%E8%A2%AB%E6%8C%87%E9%90%B3%E5%B0%84%E7%AD%86%E7%85%A7%E8%AD%A6-%E5%AE%98%E7%9C%8B%E7%95%A2%E7%89%87%E6%AE%B5%E8%B3%AA%E7%96%91%E6%9C%89%E6%84%8F%E5%9C%96%E5%82%B7%E4%BA%BA-%E8%BE%AF%E6%96%B9%E6%93%AC%E6%94%B9%E8%AA%8D%E7%BD%AA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F9-24-%25E5%25A4%25AA%25E5%25AD%2590-19-%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E7%2594%25B7%25E7%2594%259F%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258C%2587%25E9%2590%25B3%25E5%25B0%2584%25E7%25AD%2586%25E7%2585%25A7%25E8%25AD%25A6-%25E5%25AE%2598%25E7%259C%258B%25E7%2595%25A2%25E7%2589%2587%25E6%25AE%25B5%25E8%25B3%25AA%25E7%2596%2591%25E6%259C%2589%25E6%2584%258F%25E5%259C%2596%25E5%2582%25B7%25E4%25BA%25BA-%25E8%25BE%25AF%25E6%2596%25B9%25E6%2593%25AC%25E6%2594%25B9%25E8%25AA%258D%25E7%25BD%25AA%2F&d=CDYmK9DOGPUFxvwNhHfqxyF8jviwHHlsaTD6zKFHFMM%3D&h=ad8d2dac\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F9-24-%25E5%25A4%25AA%25E5%25AD%2590-19-%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E7%2594%25B7%25E7%2594%259F%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258C%2587%25E9%2590%25B3%25E5%25B0%2584%25E7%25AD%2586%25E7%2585%25A7%25E8%25AD%25A6-%25E5%25AE%2598%25E7%259C%258B%25E7%2595%25A2%25E7%2589%2587%25E6%25AE%25B5%25E8%25B3%25AA%25E7%2596%2591%25E6%259C%2589%25E6%2584%258F%25E5%259C%2596%25E5%2582%25B7%25E4%25BA%25BA-%25E8%25BE%25AF%25E6%2596%25B9%25E6%2593%25AC%25E6%2594%25B9%25E8%25AA%258D%25E7%25BD%25AA%2F&h=14c5ddcd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/court/9-24-%E5%A4%AA%E5%AD%90-19-%E6%AD%B2%E7%94%B7%E7%94%9F%E8%A2%AB%E6%8C%87%E9%90%B3%E5%B0%84%E7%AD%86%E7%85%A7%E8%AD%A6-%E5%AE%98%E7%9C%8B%E7%95%A2%E7%89%87%E6%AE%B5%E8%B3%AA%E7%96%91%E6%9C%89%E6%84%8F%E5%9C%96%E5%82%B7%E4%BA%BA-%E8%BE%AF%E6%96%B9%E6%93%AC%E6%94%B9%E8%AA%8D%E7%BD%AA/</a>"},{"pid":"893422f8c09da0cf6eb0ac2dba41e354ed50db13","tid":2495686,"uid":37869,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T10:29:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2420000/2421947/rong02--_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2420000%2F2421947%2Frong02--_1024.jpg&h=2f2f9306&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"da1e5c533f15ff78dcb8bb14def37a0551bd2d02","tid":2495686,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T10:30:40.000Z","msg":"次被告向警方做侮辱手勢，警員拍下案發經過，掃蕩時拘捕被告及另外兩名男子。<br />\n<br />\n至於第三被告 14 歲女童，控方指片中女聲「阿 sir 你支筆冇電？」是來自她，亦拍到她用鐳射筆照射警員。辯方指被告曾在現場聚集，但只是與旁人聊天，「同其他人士冇關連，唔能夠同其他在場人士串埋一齊」。"},{"pid":"ddccbe2c9eb3fd30c1bb98ff537f60ea1237a75f","tid":2495686,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T10:35:49.000Z","msg":"片段中，只手持雨傘的第一被告及14歲被告女童被拍到曾使用雷射筆。頭戴白色帽的女童手中曾發出綠光，其後坐在欄杆上說話，控方指她當時正叫：「阿sir你電筒冇電呀？阿sir？」裁判官<span class=\"red\">陳慧敏反覆觀看片段，稱：「我覺得都清楚。」</span><br />\n<br />\n次被告廖被拍到向警方舉中指，第四被告霍則被拍下吹牧童笛，但沒有片段顯示兩人用過雷射筆。<br />\n<br />\n稱「超過十支向我方向射」 事後沒有看醫生<br />\n<br />\n盤問下，吳稱自己是被雷射筆「一個重點被攻擊嘅目標」，並指雷射光束多數射向她眼部及頭部，「超過十支向我方向射」，令她雙眼不適，但她承認沒有事後看醫生。<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210419/2Q7DUP4PHFCPHAWM7CNZFI7WBA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210419%2F2Q7DUP4PHFCPHAWM7CNZFI7WBA%2F&d=CDYmK9DOGPUFxvwNhHfqxyF8jviwHHlsaTD6zKFHFMM%3D&h=ccb5bc0b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210419%2F2Q7DUP4PHFCPHAWM7CNZFI7WBA%2F&h=079ba546\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210419/2Q7DUP4PHFCPHAWM7CNZFI7WBA/</a>"},{"pid":"31ac85d9ad40899844d5e1cb6c3a02058ac022b6","tid":2495686,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T10:43:05.000Z","msg":"袋住同拎住都話有意圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f2fcc2302c13c2cad46e459107b88bb6f8668d3","tid":2495686,"uid":11793,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T10:44:51.000Z","msg":"又係呢條臭閪陳慧敏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"172c73df133633bc36d918d0a34624c9cb35629b","tid":2495686,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T10:46:51.000Z","msg":"從來無展示過點傷人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f672c22b7396a007ac9aedbfe65497ada484492f","tid":2495686,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T10:52:59.000Z","msg":"3名成年被告各自被控管有攻擊性武器，蔡和霍涉管有雷射筆，廖則被控管有雷射筆及萬用刀。<br />\n<br />\n俾佢審吹牧童笛實變軍樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />個女仔同第一被告接觸過, 條撚樣又話肯定個女仔有講啲野/用過筆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n難甩到爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3afab3de5695c8c325b4f5d703db8dd948eee170","tid":2495686,"uid":252840,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"893422f8c09